{"tid":454102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【戚家冚家剷】遭逼婚女子涉毒殺丈夫一家致最少13死","createTime":"2017-10-31T23:25:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-01T00:05:55.000Z","uid":37661,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7df2fa2a9884792251b90bdc177cbac0e8fea10b","tid":454102,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T23:25:32.000Z","msg":"巴基斯坦有遭逼婚女子涉毒殺丈夫一家致最少13死<br />\n2017-11-01 HKT 00:29<br />\n <br />\n 強迫婚姻在巴基斯坦一些貧窮落後的地區仍普遍存在。<br />\n<br />\n警方說被告今年9月被迫結婚。她上星期將有毒物質混入奶中，原本只打算毒殺丈夫，但丈夫無飲用。毒奶之後被製成當地傳統乳酪，丈夫及家人進食後中毒，最少13人死亡，14人仍然留醫。<br />\n<br />\n警方說涉案被捕的還包括一名自稱深愛被告的男子，及該名男子一名長輩。報道說，被告曾千方百計從丈夫家中逃走，但不成功。強迫婚姻在巴基斯坦一些貧窮落後的地區仍普遍存在，通常由家人促成。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1362355-20171101.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1362355-20171101.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=r%2B%2FiB006GaAC7ImnPZ1QyUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=c8751ee2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1362355-20171101.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=7b459560\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1362355-20171101.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"aaa74e89cd9b5b4a99e79fa23cc1e862a5e2572c","tid":454102,"uid":55045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T23:28:29.000Z","msg":"毒奶之後被製成當地傳統乳酪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b88f7effa369603049a2d9aca4f064dcb1f7389a","tid":454102,"uid":100150,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T23:32:30.000Z","msg":"呢度有一煲糖水，一斤砒霜，倒晒落去之後。嘩，頂你個肺吖，重杰過芝麻糊，呢啲野會有人肯飲？"},{"pid":"1e1d6ffdcca5bb3dcfb0ff0c0137838747e3e15c","tid":454102,"uid":37661,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T23:34:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢度有一煲糖水，一斤砒霜，倒晒落去之後。嘩，頂你個肺吖，重杰過芝麻糊，呢啲野會有人肯飲？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係一升牛奶，一斤砒霜。<br />\n<br />\n咁杰梗係飲唔到，咪做乳酪囉。"},{"pid":"0e009e4a770f32a24d558184059fea70ea422e86","tid":454102,"uid":30782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T23:38:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢度有一煲糖水，一斤砒霜，倒晒落去之後。嘩，頂你個肺吖，重杰過芝麻糊，呢啲野會有人肯飲？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係一升牛奶，一斤砒霜。<br />\n<br />\n咁杰梗係飲唔到，咪做乳酪囉。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63dab50ea617c689835b494fccc9e0e4619d4761","tid":454102,"uid":98261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T23:40:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢度有一煲糖水，一斤砒霜，倒晒落去之後。嘩，頂你個肺吖，重杰過芝麻糊，呢啲野會有人肯飲？</blockquote><br />\n或者戚家啲人豬頭抦，咁冇計㗎"},{"pid":"b1d78b2b1ace6f6799855bca929508517e7221eb","tid":454102,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T23:42:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"89d1aeb5b10732db4c2307c48353955493c1e48f","tid":454102,"uid":100150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T23:49:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢度有一煲糖水，一斤砒霜，倒晒落去之後。嘩，頂你個肺吖，重杰過芝麻糊，呢啲野會有人肯飲？</blockquote><br />\n或者戚家啲人豬頭抦，咁冇計㗎</blockquote><br />\n喂，唔啱你整啖呀<br />\n好野黎，飲左之後曉飛天添㗎"},{"pid":"9d21ab0f561ebc7f551c9db33ca3e9d7e2d594fb","tid":454102,"uid":84275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T23:50:59.000Z","msg":"屌你又變左有聲對白post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁佢買一斤又唔洗用晒一斤既姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b737cab4b5624fbac0966c28e2a8ead807217845","tid":454102,"uid":15954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T23:54:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你又變左有聲對白post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁佢買一斤又唔洗用晒一斤既姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但佢到搵唔到仲有批箱剩低"},{"pid":"095ddae140bef02d2b581ee3dc6938b16c785ba5","tid":454102,"uid":86893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-